de.slackspace.openkeepass.processor

Class BinaryEnricher

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.slackspace.openkeepass.processor.BinaryEnricher

  • public class BinaryEnricher
extends java.lang.Object
    Adds the raw attachment data of all nodes in a KeePass file to the nodes itself. This makes it possible to call Attachment.getData() and on the nodes to retrieve the icon data.
    See Also:
    Attachment.getData()
